Freud; the pioneer of psychoanalysis, the study of the unconscious mind.

00:00:32.217 --> 00:00:38.347
To some, he is the man who created a vitally important way of understanding the human mind.

00:00:38.657 --> 00:00:42.477
To others, he was a sex-obsessed pseudoscienst.

00:00:43.047 --> 00:00:47.657
Whatever you think of Sigmund Freud, he transformed, and in many ways

